parcel.name: AV GALLERY
parcel.label: gallery
parcel.description:
A/V GALLERY is the virtual gallery of Atomic Visual Studio, built on blockchain-based online community. As new media art group and art curator, Atomic Visual will distribute A/V original NFT artworks, as well as other NFT artworks in the form of mix-media/ audio-visual/ illustration/ music etc. by our cooperative artists.

A/V GALLERY是放射能创立的虚拟艺术馆。放射能以新媒体艺术创作团体及策展人的身份，发行由放射能原创的NFT艺术作品，以及合作艺术家的NFT艺术作品，包括但不限于混合媒介、音视觉、插画、音乐等形式。
